metadata.name: W01VE5
metadata.description:
The rage is visible in their eyes, but where can it come from? 
Does it come from their condition of synthetic beings, always taken from above by humanity? Or does it come from their will to free themselves from the chains created by this merciless humanity? 
Humanity is about to live a great social upheaval... the synthetic beings are rising all over the world wearing these strange shapes on their face, a symbol of their will.
